         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Botanical Gardens, Melbourne, ¶ September 14th, 1859. ¶ My dear Sir — ¶  ¶ The great Humboldt, had he been spared to us, would have attained this day his 90th year. Very considerately the German Assoc...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">59.09.14</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To John Macadam</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found. For the text given here, see B60.06.03.</p>
               </note>Botanical Gardens, Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">September 14th, 1859.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The great Humboldt, had he been spared to us, would have attained this day his 90th year. Very considerately the German Association has chosen this day for a solemn festival in memory of him whom we must regard as the greatest genius of this century. Responding on this occasion to a request of my countrymen, to deliver one of the necrologs,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">B59.09.02.</p>
               </note> I am unable to be present at the meeting of the Philosophical Institute convened for this evening.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours most regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="font-variant: small-caps; ">Ferdinand Mueller</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">John Macadam, Esq., M.D.,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Honorary Secretary of the Philosophical Institute of Victoria<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M's letter was read at the ordinary meeting of the Philosophical Institute of Victoria held on 14 September 1859.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
